id: pmc-70yk
title: Retry transient package-install cleanup
description: "The Greptile T-Rex sandbox for release PR #69 intermittently hit ENOTEMPTY while the package-install smoke fixture removed its unique temporary tree. Authoritative release and post-release CI passed, so this is a cleanup race/flakiness defect rather than a product failure."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 2
tags: []
created_at: "2026-07-14T01:52:06.858Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-14T01:56:32.131Z"
closed_at: "2026-07-14T01:54:25.791Z"
author: codex
acceptance_criteria: Package-install fixture cleanup uses bounded Node-native retry semantics; Repeated focused package-install smoke tests pass; Full release gate remains green; The pm item links the Greptile evidence and affected test.
risk: low
confidence: high
release: v2026.7.14-1
severity: medium
environment: "Greptile T-Rex run 14331123 on PR #69, Node 24.18.0/npm 11.16.0; local and GitHub Actions release gates pass."
repro_steps: Run the full release gate repeatedly in clean sandboxes; observe that test/generator.test.ts package-install smoke cleanup can fail with ENOTEMPTY after child commands complete.
resolution: "Use fs.rmSync recursive cleanup with five 100ms linear-backoff retries, preserving failure after the bounded window."
expected_result: Fixture cleanup tolerates transient ENOTEMPTY/EBUSY conditions and never makes an otherwise-passing gate flaky.
actual_result: A single recursive rmSync attempt can terminate the suite on transient ENOTEMPTY.
affected_version: 2026.7.14
fixed_version: 2026.7.14-1
component: tests
comments[3]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-14T01:53:34.532Z",codex,Focused package-install smoke passed six consecutive clean-fixture executions after adding Node-native recursive cleanup retries. The final visible run completed in 6.2s; transient cleanup failures remain bounded and persistent errors still propagate.
  "2026-07-14T01:54:25.556Z",codex,"Full pm-linked verification passed: affected smoke test plus release:check, 141/141 tests, zero production vulnerabilities, 37 expected package files, and current changelog."
  "2026-07-14T01:56:32.130Z",codex,"Accepted pre-push Greptile review 65d1ae13-2b94-43eb-a9ab-f6778be60e48 P2: use Node's 100ms default retry interval with five linear-backoff retries (~1.5s total headroom) for loaded CI runners."
